snippet.title: Koropokkur In Love ~ A Little Fairy's Tale ~ Kickstarter PV
snippet.description:
Koropokkur-our very first project as a developer-is now LIVE on Kickstarter!
After 10 years of localizing visual novels, we're proud to venture into their creation! With art by Itaru Hinoue, we hope this little fairy tale brings you a warm smile. 

More information can be found on the Kickstarter page and our blog!

Kickstarter: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1231894392/koropokkur-in-love-a-little-fairys-tale

Blog: http://blog.mangagamer.org/2018/03/06/koropokkur-page-is-now-live-on-kickstarter/
